<aside class="col-md-4 blog-sidebar">
    <div class="p-3 mb-3 bg-light rounded">
        <h4 class="font-italic">Sharing in giving</h4>
        <p class="mb-0">Knowledge is powerful only if shared with others.
        This blog aims not only to share information regarding me but also contribute with tips tools and
        tricks for software development.
        </p>
    </div>
        <%= source_helper("alert alert-info") %>
